{"tid":808061,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女子網上結識自稱工程師　疑被騙1億8千萬元　","createTime":"2018-09-06T05:05:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-09T07:20:15.000Z","uid":71215,"like":34,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"6ef3ea32bf30810b56a0c905aa028a8fc8c7c957","tid":808061,"uid":71215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T05:05:12.000Z","msg":"一名女子懷疑受騙，涉及金額1億8千萬元。案件列作「以欺騙手段取得財產」，暫時未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n該名女子在上月初報案，指在網上交友平台結識一名自稱為身處海外的工程師，對方在2014年5月至今年7月期間，多次向受害人表示自己生意周轉困難，向受害人索取金錢，受害人按指示多次匯款後懷疑受騙，於是報案。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，受害人年齡超過50歲，屬富裕人士，她在交友平台與自稱是專業人士的外國人認識，兩人並無見過面，今次是有紀錄以來最大宗的網上情緣騙案。<br />\n<br />\n邊度黎咁多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53be1c1fc1cc2eedd4b95ae5b3a0155d509d0452","tid":808061,"uid":25900,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T05:06:23.000Z","msg":"又係女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26436a7891a33c3520f11d3d1699497537702086","tid":808061,"uid":32577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T05:06:42.000Z","msg":"一億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3237b739e6471a76b16fd747a5e48e3e742fa64","tid":808061,"uid":21028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T05:07:26.000Z","msg":"呢個世界真係 咁撚蠢可以有一億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8979a5d4b699ebde3f4a082287eaaf09a6de03b5","tid":808061,"uid":35106,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T05:10:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁有米不如包隻鴨玩下就算啦"},{"pid":"0b430aaf8ee2115f907d4fea47b8c9fcfd7c5234","tid":808061,"uid":119778,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T05:10:53.000Z","msg":"然而女人話男人淨係識用碌鳩諗野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/fac